{"tid":2057644,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【出去又送頭】【冷氣軍師】【分化】你同我玩埋佢喇","createTime":"2020-06-09T14:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:49:01.000Z","uid":273355,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"662816ee6d9563166527f435a378622ae3babef5","tid":2057644,"uid":273355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千萬唔好慣咗用負面字眼嚟形容自己人<br />\n因為語言會限制你嘅思想</span></span><br />\n如果你一睇到手足做唔合自己心意嘅事<br />\n就又送頭又冷氣軍師咁形容自己人<br />\n慢慢我哋就會無咗手足呢個概念<br />\n我知道睇唔順眼一嘢屌出嚟係人之常情<br />\n但大家為咗大家<br />\n忍忍口<br />\n試下改一改用字<br />\n例如：<br />\n送頭 -&gt; 被濫捕<br />\n冷氣軍師/和理非 -&gt; 文宣組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而對家用字就應該唔用中性或正面用字<br />\n警察 -&gt; 狗<br />\n中國 -&gt; 共匪<br />\n督察 -&gt; 白衫狗<br />\n政府 -&gt; 中共傀儡<br />\n<br />\nquote 一下眾新聞<br />\n//George Orwell 的著名小說《1984》中，極權國家Oceania 創造了另一套語言系統Newspeak 來取代傳統英語。當中政府不希望人民擁有的思想會從Newspeak 詞彙中刪除或改變原有的意思，例如democracy 和freedom 便不會出現在Newspeak 中。另外，free 一字亦在Newspeak 中改變了用途，它只可解作「沒有」的意義，例如&quot;This dog is free from lice&quot;，但不能再包含政治（politically free）和思想（intellectually free）層面的自由。當沒有了這些詞彙，只需要幾代人的時間，「自由」這個抽象概念便能由人民中連根拔起。語言是思想的載體，沒有了語言思想便無法表達，更加不能傳播。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/9932/%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80-%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%B5%B1%E6%B2%BB-%E8%A9%B1%E8%AA%9E%E6%AC%8A-9932/%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80%E5%BB%BA%E6%A7%8B%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%AA%E7%90%86%E5%BB%BA%E6%A7%8B%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F9932%2F%25E8%25AA%259E%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%25B2%25BB-%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25AA%259E%25E6%25AC%258A-9932%2F%25E8%25AA%259E%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25A7%258B%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%25AD%25AA%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25A7%258B%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%258A&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=0d6733e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/9932/%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80-%E6%A5%B5%E6%AC%8A%E7%B5%B1%E6%B2%BB-%E8%A9%B1%E8%AA%9E%E6%AC%8A-9932/%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80%E5%BB%BA%E6%A7%8B%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%AA%E7%90%86%E5%BB%BA%E6%A7%8B%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%8A</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n不分化不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb7f1c47bd6bf36eb286486ec4b02aaa1be1589b","tid":2057644,"uid":273355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790e0d60b75f26dc8e6401835826471a07ffcb56","tid":2057644,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"cdc2c388b2ff79f5033737cd9d4eb2797e11eaed","tid":2057644,"uid":273355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"790e0d60b75f26dc8e6401835826471a07ffcb56","tid":2057644,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"認同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"幫手推推可以嗎<br />\n好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8330a1e4b189fc7ede3939668c87f310b565a778","tid":2057644,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師==&gt;策略師 <br />\n點解要用貶義稱呼手足？"},{"pid":"d1934ef78d6687647d5ab90a8a438d240e84f5d0","tid":2057644,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"中國==&gt;中国==&gt;支那"},{"pid":"29ba4653d48d95b56b1935809d77b1686f44fa3f","tid":2057644,"uid":215501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"因為有堆真五毛